      "content": "### 2008: Founding at KIT\n\nA group of students — Moritz Meenen, Jan Henric Stönner, Martin Mitscher, Tobias Griesshaber, and Maximilian Engelken — founded the new university group \"PionierGarage\" at KIT. Regular Tuesday meetings became the main activity, with founders invited for \"Meet-the-Founder\" sessions so students could get first-hand entrepreneurship experience.\n\n",
